izard)</span><hr size=1> Hi there - interesting information....<br>
<br>
I too am a Wizard from EQ - level 55 on Veeshan.<br>
<br>
When I got DAoC, I deliberately made a Cleric as my main as I was just too burned from EQ and my investment into EQ to ever try a casting class like that again. I made the choice as a support player for investment purposes.<br>
<br>
I am not sure what server you are on - but within my guild in DAoC, our Wizards are very much worthwhile. As a Cleric, I intentionally buff my wizzie buds whenever possible. As far as damage - I have no idea as to a comparason. <br>
<br>
EQ has been out for quite a while and I feel it is the BEST game in the category. I do, however, prefer DAoC as it allows for much more diversity in class and character selections. EQ has cookie-cutter classes that are stereotyped even before you create that level 1 character. Depending on the server you are on, as well as a myriad of things, within EQ, investing your time into a Cleric, Enchanter, or Warrior will bring about a reward from levels 1 - 60. Other classes are ok, but you lower your chances of advancement, groupage, and end game play with most other class selections. I mean - it can be done and has, but it is definately a harder path with less rewards in the end.<br>
<br>
DAoC allows you to put your training points into different branches of study within each character. I know Wizards that spec in Fire - others Ice. You have no idea what extra spells/abilities you will get and use along each branch you choose and how they will test out in game. I like that. No cookie-cutter chars with pre-conceived notions. You have no idea when you group with a Wizard on where they have put their points into and how that will affect gameplay.<br>
<br>
As far as fast damage in DAoC - I am not sure where you hunt - but there is a definate time and place where my biscuits have been saved from fast damage casting Wizzies. <br>
<br>
From seeing the Wizards from my guild in combat - trust me - I ALWAYS want one in my group - and I am a Cleric. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
Amir Ar'Rahmanu<br>
34 Highlander Cleric<br>
Albion - Galahad server<br>
